    "body": "So you want to show the name if it’s there and otherwise the actingvalue? In this case you should add an \r\n\r\n```js\r\nif (name.matchedWords.length >0) // render name\r\nelse // render the other thing\r\n```\r\n\r\nThat was just pseudocode, but it should be quite close ",
